name: IWR-BelleDelphineUltimate
description:
Hi everyone ! For those who know me from discord , you already know that my loras are carefully perfected, for the others I invite you to read instead :

This lora has been trained with more than 8000 unique images and it's what i'm proud to call the ultimate Belle Delphine Lora .

-- Use with Str 0.9 or 1

-- It has really strong irl style so it can be used with semi realistic models but it works amazing with irl models since it's intended to be used with those , if you want an anime Belle , there are other loras out there.
-- I recommend using the Verisimilitude model for it's realism , eyes and anatomy.
-- Trigger word is obviusly : Belle Delphine

I hope that you will like my work since it takes most of my (little...) free time.

Commissions are open on my part if you want me to make something you can visit my Ko-fi page if you like :)

Post and comment if you want , i try to help as much as i can :D
